about.summary: Download and import of 'OpenStreetMap' ('OSM') data as 'sf' or 'sp' objects.  'OSM' data are extracted from the 'Overpass' web server and processed with very fast 'C++' routines for return to 'R'.

name: r-osmdata
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.3' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-osmdata
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/osmdata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/osmdata/osmdata_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 98dd9520e52bab445af22288d3f1c9b12c5acf081b9e40410171ea23d173a7a8

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.4
    - r-curl
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-lubridate
    - r-magrittr
    - r-rvest
    - r-sp
    - r-tibble
    - r-xml2
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.4
    - r-curl
    - r-httr
    - r-jsonlite
    - r-lubridate
    - r-magrittr
    - r-rvest
    - r-sp
    - r-tibble
    - r-xml2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('osmdata')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('osmdata')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://docs.ropensci.org/osmdata (website) https://github.com/ropensci/osmdata (devel)
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Download and import of 'OpenStreetMap' ('OSM') data as 'sf' or 'sp' objects.  'OSM'
    data are extracted from the 'Overpass' web server and processed with very fast 'C++'
    routines for return to 'R'.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - xhochy
